{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"relevant programmer","author":"Ashok Dudhade"}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"f4b15c9d-c2a0-50e2-9315-5d8db45c5b14","excerpt":"Prerequisites: Nodejs yarn create-react-app There are so many posts available for creating react app with yarn workspaces, but I have not…","html":"<p>Prerequisites:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Nodejs</li>\n<li>yarn</li>\n<li>create-react-app</li>\n</ul>\n<p>There are so many posts available for creating react app with yarn workspaces, but I have not came across any article with typescript.</p>\n<p>To create a sample app we will use <code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app</code> utility.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">create-react-app typescript-react-yarn-worspaces --scripts-version=react-scripts-ts\n\ncd typescript-react-yarn-worspaces</code></pre></div>\n<p>Eject app to unpack all configuration files into our application. This is required to include yarn workspaces directory in typescript configurations.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn eject</code></pre></div>\n<p>It will display a message “Are you sure you want to eject? This action is permanent.” Press ‘y’ to confirm. It should unpack configuration files.</p>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\"></code></p>\n<h3>Why yarn workspaces?</h3>\n<p>Multiple reusable packages can be adding in single repository which can depend on each other with single yarn lock file at root directory. This also has benefit of always referring to latest package source code.</p>\n<h3>Code changes</h3>\n<p>Open new ‘typescript-react-yarn-worspaces’ directory in your favorite IDE.</p>\n<p>Create a directory for packages at root level (<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces\\packages</code>).</p>\n<p>Open package.json file and add worspaces details.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&quot;workspaces&quot;: [&quot;packages/*&quot;]</code></pre></div>\n<p>Modify webpack configuration to include “packages” directory to include for build and watch.</p>\n<p>Add packagesSrc in paths.js file. (<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces/config/paths.js</code>)</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-1132f.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 12.512413108242304%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"packages source entry\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-526de.png 885w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/paths-01-50a4289fbd67b3eb90ccb79ce63880e1-1132f.png 2014w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Modify webpack.config.dev.js to include packages directory.(<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces/config/webpack.config.dev.js</code>)</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-b53c2.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 14.754098360655737%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"dev 01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-526de.png 885w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/dev-01-408baf1961217aefbb2f4b5907b461c6-b53c2.png 2562w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-a0c46.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 20.890688259109314%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"dev 02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-526de.png 885w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/dev-02-24af1ec620656b8907544559cb02d1dc-a0c46.png 2470w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-b8876.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 25.956061838893408%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"dev 03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-526de.png 885w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/dev-03-ffa031caa7b682268a186e3833279945-b8876.png 2458w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-a6e73.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 13.647246608140462%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"dev 04\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-526de.png 885w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/dev-04-08175679660ba597f943e4c483481972-a6e73.png 2506w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Modify webpack.config.prod.js to include packages directory.(<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces/config/webpack.config.prod.js</code>)</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-a0c46.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 14.331983805668017%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"prod 01\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-526de.png 885w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/prod-01-53c8987a84bd0a9f0e369520b35764ad-a0c46.png 2470w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-30ac1.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 17.42671009771987%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"prod 02\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-526de.png 885w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/prod-02-43ef4e5f357caf016af8204daaae29a7-30ac1.png 2456w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    \n\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-a0c46.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 13.441295546558704%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"prod 03\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-526de.png 885w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/prod-03-87a08efd73bf4e7398dd2b883aedd64c-a0c46.png 2470w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>Now let’s create a reusable <code class=\"language-text\">Header</code> component for the application. Create a ‘header’ directory inside packages(<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces\\packages\\header</code>) and add below files.</p>\n<p>Add package.json file(<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces\\packages\\header\\package.json</code>).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">{\n    &quot;name&quot;: &quot;@my-app/header&quot;,\n    &quot;version&quot;: &quot;0.1.0&quot;,\n    &quot;private&quot;: true,\n    &quot;dependencies&quot;: {\n        &quot;react&quot;: &quot;^16.5.2&quot;,\n        &quot;react-dom&quot;: &quot;^16.5.2&quot;\n    },\n    &quot;devDependencies&quot;: {\n        &quot;@types/node&quot;: &quot;^10.11.4&quot;,\n        &quot;@types/react&quot;: &quot;^16.4.16&quot;,\n        &quot;@types/react-dom&quot;: &quot;^16.0.8&quot;,\n        &quot;typescript&quot;: &quot;^3.1.1&quot;\n    }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>Add index.tsx file(<code class=\"language-text\">typescript-react-yarn-worspaces\\packages\\header\\index.tsx</code>).</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import * as React from &#39;react&#39;;\nimport &#39;./App.css&#39;;\n\nexport class Header extends React.Component {\n  public render() {\n    return (\n        &lt;header className=&quot;App-header&quot;&gt;\n          &lt;h1 className=&quot;App-title&quot;&gt;Header from packages&lt;/h1&gt;\n        &lt;/header&gt;\n    );\n  }\n}</code></pre></div>\n<p>Modify root package json to add header package dependency along with App.tsx file.</p>\n<p>package.json dependency</p>\n<p>\n  <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-3f416.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n  \n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block; ; max-width: 590px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 13.012295081967212%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;\"\n        alt=\"package-json\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-fb8a0.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-1a291.png 148w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-2bc4a.png 295w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-fb8a0.png 590w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-526de.png 885w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-fa2eb.png 1180w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-08f6a.png 1770w,\n/static/package-json-fbb0a4596b51e8109ee3928eb42f1d11-3f416.png 1952w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  \n  </a>\n    </p>\n<p>App.tsx</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">import { Header } from &#39;@my-app/header&#39;;\nimport * as React from &#39;react&#39;;\nimport &#39;./App.css&#39;;\n\nclass App extends React.Component {\n  public render() {\n    return (\n      &lt;div className=&quot;App&quot;&gt;\n        &lt;Header/&gt;\n        &lt;p className=&quot;App-intro&quot;&gt;\n          To get started, edit &lt;code&gt;src/App.tsx&lt;/code&gt; and save to reload.\n        &lt;/p&gt;\n      &lt;/div&gt;\n    );\n  }\n}\n\nexport default App;</code></pre></div>\n<p>To start app do as below.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">yarn install\nyarn start</code></pre></div>\n<p>Code is available at <a href=\"https://github.com/ashokdudhade/typescript-react-yarn-worspaces\">github</a></p>","frontmatter":{"title":"Typescript react app with yarn workspaces","date":"October 09, 2018"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/typescript-react-app-with-yarn-worspaces/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/docker-for-programmers/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Docker for programmers"}},"next":null}}